and with a loss of Pounds 466,000 in the first half of 1993. Turnover grew
to Pounds 12.3m (Pounds 10.7m).
Earnings per share came out at 1.8p (1.3p losses) and the company is
resuming dividend payments with an interim distribution of 0.35p. Last
year's final was passed, although there was an interim of 0.45p.
