<TEXT>
Astra, the fast-growing Swedish pharmaceutical group, yesterday moved to
enhance its profile in the US by obtaining a listing on the over-the-counter
market in New York.
The company said American depository receipts matching its A and B shares
already quoted in Stockholm and London began trading yesterday.
Astra, which last week reported a 23 per cent rise in pre-tax profits in the
