</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
PT Freeport Indonesia, the Indonesian mining unit of Freeport-McMoRan Copper
&amp; Gold of the US, has sold a group of its non-mining assets for about
Dollars 77m, AP-DJ reports from New Orleans. The deal is one of a series of
completed and planned asset sales.
