<HEADLINE>
FT  08 SEP 94 / UK Company News: Adscene
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A strong performance from its publishing side helped Adscene Group to lift
pre-tax profits by 45 per cent from Pounds 2.1m to Pounds 3.05m for the year
ended May 31. Turnover of the group, which also has printing interests, rose
13 per cent to Pounds 15.8m.
Earnings per share rose 37 per cent from 10.1p to 13.8p and the recommended
final dividend of 4p (3.2p) makes a total pay-out of 6.5p (5p).
</TEXT>
